        {
            "name": "Tactics",
            "type": "section",
            "html": "<b>Base Statistics</b> When not raging and not affected by <i>barkskin</i>, the champion\u2019s statistics are <b>AC</b> 21, touch 11, flat-footed 18; <b>hp </b>105; <b>Fort </b>+12, <b>Will </b>+8; <b>Melee</b><i>+1 trident</i> +16/+11 (1d8+10), claw +13 (1d4+3), mwk spiked heavy steel shield +16 (1d6+6), bite +13 (1d4+3) or 4 claws +15 (1d4+6), bite +15 (1d4+6); <b>Ranged </b>mwk heavy crossbow +13 (1d10/19\u201320); <b>Str </b>22, <b>Con </b>17; <b>CMB </b>+15, <b>CMD </b>28; <b>Skills </b>Intimidate +18, Swim +25."
        },
        {
            "name": "Ecology",
            "type": "section",
            "html": "<b>Environment</b> temperate or warm ocean"
        },
        {
            "name": "Description",
            "type": "section",
            "html": "These sahuagin revel in their rage and blood frenzy."
        }
